WEBVTT

01:39.539 --> 01:43.250
[Road to Success]

01:44.820 --> 01:47.780
[Episode 17]

02:01.040 --> 02:02.760
Good evening, Wang Fa.

02:04.640 --> 02:05.790
I have seldom

02:05.790 --> 02:07.970
recorded this kind of stuff before.

02:07.990 --> 02:09.860
So I feel a bit shy.

02:12.000 --> 02:12.800
First of all,

02:13.430 --> 02:15.720
thank you so much
for your company recently

02:15.470 --> 02:19.360
[No.08, Ziwei Road]

02:16.870 --> 02:20.079
and for coaching the players.

02:25.400 --> 02:27.680
To you, these players

02:27.880 --> 02:30.280
might just be passing strangers.

02:31.360 --> 02:34.620
You helped them like casually
rescuing drowning cats,

02:35.120 --> 02:37.720
picking them up
and letting them dry in the sun.

02:39.650 --> 02:40.810
Wang Fa.

02:40.829 --> 02:42.180
But you know what?

02:43.000 --> 02:44.400
For a kitten,

02:45.120 --> 02:46.720
being bathed in the sunlight

02:47.060 --> 02:48.940
is the happiest

02:48.960 --> 02:50.610
and safest thing in its life.

02:51.940 --> 02:53.250
Thank you so much.

03:13.150 --> 03:14.180
Thank you.

04:06.210 --> 04:08.300
Wanxing Lin.

04:08.550 --> 04:10.700
[Wanxing Lin's E-mail]

04:12.470 --> 04:14.000
Who registered this email?

04:22.480 --> 04:24.470
[Support all business and
personal email accounts]

04:26.950 --> 04:30.110
[Support all business and
personal email accounts]

04:30.140 --> 04:30.210
[Verifying]

04:33.040 --> 04:34.930
[Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

04:35.080 --> 04:35.900
[President's Office of
Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

04:35.930 --> 04:36.900
[Letter of Appointment from the Bureau]

04:36.920 --> 04:37.930
[Notice Regarding
the Appointment of the New Head Coach]

05:00.930 --> 05:03.410
[Notice Regarding
the Appointment of the New Head Coach]

05:02.130 --> 05:04.070
Coach Liu Chuanguang is appointed

05:04.110 --> 05:06.640
as the head coach
of Yongchuan Hengjiu Club.

05:06.280 --> 05:10.130
[Notice Regarding
the Appointment of the New Head Coach]

05:07.550 --> 05:09.630
Wang Fa isn't

05:09.740 --> 05:11.740
the new coach of Yongchuan Hengjiu?

05:13.180 --> 05:15.520
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

05:16.160 --> 05:20.410
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

05:21.000 --> 05:22.960
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

05:23.480 --> 05:28.380
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
I chanced upon ♪

05:28.550 --> 05:31.090
[School Area]

05:28.970 --> 05:31.770
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

05:32.290 --> 05:35.710
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

05:36.690 --> 05:39.700
♪ I once dreamed of something beautiful ♪

05:40.360 --> 05:44.030
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

05:45.050 --> 05:47.480
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

05:48.120 --> 05:51.980
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

05:50.090 --> 05:50.800
Stop.

05:53.170 --> 05:55.590
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

05:56.260 --> 05:59.970
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

06:00.830 --> 06:03.470
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

06:04.150 --> 06:07.920
♪ Let the ending remain with
questions unanswered ♪

06:08.720 --> 06:11.290
♪ No need to prove it with promises ♪

06:12.270 --> 06:16.030
♪ The dusk when we once vowed
to stay together ♪

06:16.980 --> 06:19.410
♪ No need to cling to forever ♪

06:19.920 --> 06:23.350
♪ Allow parting to happen quietly ♪

06:24.660 --> 06:27.560
♪ The inner voice hidden in the origami ♪

06:28.550 --> 06:34.050
♪ Each scratch and line
is proof of beauty ♪

06:41.159 --> 06:41.970
Your clothes.

06:42.150 --> 06:43.200
Sit up straight.

06:44.630 --> 06:47.390
Come on, let's start from the right.

06:47.390 --> 06:48.390
First one, Zheng Feiyang.

06:48.390 --> 06:50.270
Come on.

06:50.870 --> 06:53.190
Coach, when you first showed up,

06:53.190 --> 06:54.870
we all thought you were a fraud.

06:54.870 --> 06:57.600
You pretended to know about football
just to hit on Ms. Lin.

06:57.600 --> 06:59.390
But we didn't expect that
you weren't pretending.

06:59.390 --> 07:01.060
You really know football.

07:01.310 --> 07:03.070
It really felt like hitting the jackpot.

07:03.070 --> 07:03.830
At first, I was wondering

07:03.830 --> 07:05.830
why someone so amazing
came to teach us.

07:05.830 --> 07:08.070
We wouldn't even dare
dream of such luck before.

07:08.070 --> 07:08.430
Yeah.

07:08.430 --> 07:09.630
We have to thank you.

07:09.630 --> 07:10.950
Yes, Coach.

07:11.360 --> 07:12.390
Next one.

07:12.390 --> 07:13.310
Let me do it.

07:13.310 --> 07:14.240
Come on.

07:14.830 --> 07:15.750
Coach.

07:15.750 --> 07:17.560
I know that you might be

07:17.590 --> 07:19.030
quite busy later on.

07:19.050 --> 07:20.490
But it's fine

07:20.520 --> 07:22.740
if you come back to guide us occasionally.

07:22.740 --> 07:24.560
Remember to come back.

07:24.870 --> 07:26.160
-Remember to come back.
-Yes.

07:26.160 --> 07:27.510
-Come on, Qi Liang, Qi Liang.
-Yes.

07:27.510 --> 07:28.270
Coach.

07:28.950 --> 07:31.390
Thank you for making up
for many of our regrets.

07:31.390 --> 07:32.270
You...

07:33.040 --> 07:35.360
You are like a durian.

07:35.360 --> 07:37.190
Although you look grumpy,

07:37.190 --> 07:39.070
you really taught us a lot.

07:39.570 --> 07:40.770
Forever Mr. Winfred.

07:41.720 --> 07:42.920
You are amazing.

07:43.630 --> 07:44.750
Next one.

07:44.750 --> 07:46.080
Wen Chengye, your turn.

07:49.950 --> 07:50.950
Stop pretending.

07:54.950 --> 07:56.390
Next time we meet,

07:56.390 --> 07:58.190
I will become even stronger than before.

07:58.190 --> 07:59.190
Just wait and see.

07:59.680 --> 08:01.190
As if we won't get stronger.

08:01.190 --> 08:02.950
Boss, your turn.

08:04.300 --> 08:05.270
-Coach.
-Use a handsome gesture.

08:05.270 --> 08:06.070
Okay.

08:06.830 --> 08:08.360
Well...

08:08.360 --> 08:09.390
Coach,

08:09.390 --> 08:10.830
thank you.

08:10.830 --> 08:13.190
Thank you for going through
so much trouble

08:13.190 --> 08:14.750
to train us to this level,

08:16.070 --> 08:17.600
leading us to defeat Ning'an

08:17.600 --> 08:18.840
and Lyujing.

08:21.470 --> 08:22.980
Thank you and Ms. Lin.

08:23.430 --> 08:25.510
After you talked with my dad that day,

08:26.190 --> 08:27.830
he changed a lot.

08:28.950 --> 08:29.750
In my whole life,

08:29.750 --> 08:31.670
the happiest thing is meeting you,

08:31.670 --> 08:33.120
a great coach.

08:33.750 --> 08:36.159
That's enough, okay.

08:36.179 --> 08:36.890
Zhi Hui.

08:38.020 --> 08:39.039
Coach.

08:39.320 --> 08:41.870
I checked your birth chart before.

08:42.309 --> 08:45.120
The fortune star is shining
on you this year.

08:45.720 --> 08:48.270
You will meet your true love here

08:48.270 --> 08:49.670
and find real happiness.

08:51.060 --> 08:53.420
I didn't expect you to run away now.

08:53.440 --> 08:54.320
But

08:54.960 --> 08:56.850
this is also my first mistake.

08:57.020 --> 08:57.900
Don't worry.

08:57.930 --> 08:59.430
When you come back next time,

08:59.430 --> 09:01.360
I'll read your fortune seriously.

09:01.400 --> 09:02.990
Then, let's do it next time.

09:03.180 --> 09:04.630
Chen.

09:06.390 --> 09:06.960
Coach.

09:07.870 --> 09:09.440
I knew you earlier than they did.

09:09.440 --> 09:10.200
You helped Ms. Lin

09:10.200 --> 09:12.130
expose that scammer on the field.

09:12.150 --> 09:13.510
She told me all about it.

09:14.270 --> 09:15.950
Actually, before I met you,

09:16.070 --> 09:17.840
for a long time, I had

09:17.840 --> 09:19.500
lost my passion for football.

09:20.160 --> 09:21.490
But after meeting you,

09:21.520 --> 09:22.970
I realized

09:23.510 --> 09:24.910
football is my true love.

09:25.200 --> 09:26.600
You're just an accident.

09:28.320 --> 09:29.180
Come on, speak.

09:31.320 --> 09:32.000
Coach.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.080
During this time,

09:34.080 --> 09:36.210
thank you so much for taking care of us.

09:37.750 --> 09:39.150
I never thought that

09:39.510 --> 09:41.710
I could still play football with you all

09:41.960 --> 09:43.820
and win matches with my brothers.

09:45.080 --> 09:46.390
It really felt like

09:46.390 --> 09:48.390
we were in a dream.

09:49.960 --> 09:52.240
Thank you, Coach.

09:53.370 --> 09:54.980
Next. Fu.

09:55.680 --> 09:56.590
Fu.

09:57.250 --> 09:58.490
Make it a bit longer.

09:59.170 --> 10:00.050
Captain.

10:02.630 --> 10:03.390
Coach.

10:04.360 --> 10:06.220
I actually have a lot to say to you.

10:08.630 --> 10:11.290
Do you know the feeling
of suddenly having hope?

10:13.240 --> 10:13.840
It's like,

10:13.840 --> 10:15.630
on a pitch-black road,

10:16.600 --> 10:17.630
I was just spinning in circles

10:17.630 --> 10:19.480
and couldn't see anything clearly.

10:19.480 --> 10:21.150
But you suddenly appeared

10:21.150 --> 10:22.670
like a beacon.

10:23.270 --> 10:24.390
Then, I knew

10:24.390 --> 10:26.030
I had to go towards you.

10:31.360 --> 10:34.690
There's actually something
I've always wanted to tell you.

10:35.120 --> 10:36.270
One day,

10:37.610 --> 10:40.400
I will make us your pride.

10:43.510 --> 10:44.630
That's too cheesy.

10:44.630 --> 10:45.670
Lu. Lu.

10:45.670 --> 10:46.390
Next.

10:46.390 --> 10:48.270
My turn.

10:48.270 --> 10:49.800
I thought you wanted to cry.

10:50.790 --> 10:52.440
Coach, you're leaving.

10:52.440 --> 10:54.300
We really can't bear to see you go.

10:54.840 --> 10:56.700
But we will definitely play well.

10:56.720 --> 10:59.440
Next time we'll show you how good we are.

11:00.910 --> 11:02.750
He's so nervous
that he can't even speak clearly.

11:02.750 --> 11:04.580
We also got you a gift,

11:04.610 --> 11:05.720
but it's a bit ugly.

11:07.290 --> 11:08.640
[Chen Jianghe] [Zheng Ren] [Feng Suo]

11:07.680 --> 11:09.200
Ta-da!

11:08.670 --> 11:10.330
[Zhi Hui] [Qin Ao] [Fu Xinshu]

11:09.510 --> 11:11.320
These are our signatures.

11:10.350 --> 11:12.130
[Yu Ming] [Qi Liang] [Wen Chengye]

11:12.150 --> 11:13.720
[Zheng Feiyang] [Lin Lu]

11:13.510 --> 11:14.670
Coach?

11:14.670 --> 11:16.390
Are you the kind that teaches
kids to play football?

11:16.390 --> 11:18.390
Coach, we have something for you.

11:19.750 --> 11:22.270
If I force professional tactics
on you now,

11:22.270 --> 11:23.030
you will fall.

11:23.030 --> 11:23.870
-No.
-No.

11:23.870 --> 11:24.870
Coach, we can do this.

11:24.870 --> 11:26.150
-Yes, Coach.
-We can do it.

11:26.150 --> 11:28.280
Do you want to go to Yongchuan Hengjiu?

11:28.990 --> 11:30.230
If so,

11:30.270 --> 11:32.130
just give it to us straight, okay?

11:33.780 --> 11:34.660
Without you,

11:35.290 --> 11:36.600
we'll continue to play football.

11:36.600 --> 11:37.940
Even without you,

11:37.960 --> 11:39.300
we still have ourselves.

11:39.300 --> 11:40.660
Then let's keep playing football

11:40.660 --> 11:41.510
and win the championship together.

11:41.510 --> 11:42.430
-Kick!
-Kick!

11:42.460 --> 11:43.150
Kick to the end.

11:43.150 --> 11:44.610
and win the championship.

12:06.270 --> 12:08.550
Come on.

12:08.960 --> 12:09.550
Come on.

12:12.160 --> 12:13.010
Coach,

12:13.350 --> 12:16.230
we love you!

12:28.190 --> 12:29.390
You are really smart.

12:30.370 --> 12:32.280
You know that in the face of money,

12:32.740 --> 12:35.140
people easily lose the courage
to speak up.

12:35.870 --> 12:38.250
You chose the best way to shut us up

12:38.420 --> 12:40.280
and stop us from holding you back.

12:51.080 --> 12:54.510
You are not the new coach
of Yongchuan Hengjiu Club at all.

12:56.160 --> 12:57.090
You are leaving,

12:57.960 --> 12:59.390
not to leave us,

13:00.120 --> 13:01.510
but to leave the pitch,

13:02.370 --> 13:03.110
right?

13:18.040 --> 13:19.040
Let's have a talk.

13:41.270 --> 13:42.930
I am indeed leaving the pitch.

13:43.390 --> 13:44.320
Why?

13:50.340 --> 13:51.130
Wang Fa.

13:53.690 --> 13:55.450
I know you are very determined

13:57.270 --> 13:58.360
and cutting off all possibilities of

13:58.360 --> 14:00.120
changing your mind.

14:02.960 --> 14:04.480
I just want to know

14:06.690 --> 14:07.900
your real reason.

14:07.930 --> 14:09.460
Because I don't deserve it.

14:13.750 --> 14:15.350
I don't deserve to stay here.

14:20.030 --> 14:21.280
Is it because of

14:21.850 --> 14:24.380
that little boy
who gave up playing football?

14:26.330 --> 14:28.260
He never gave up playing football.

14:32.720 --> 14:35.420
On the contrary, he gave up everything,

14:37.480 --> 14:39.610
including himself, to play football.

14:46.510 --> 14:47.670
He jumped

14:53.270 --> 14:54.750
off the roof.

14:58.750 --> 15:00.280
He fell right in front of me.

15:03.510 --> 15:04.550
[Jason]

15:04.570 --> 15:05.800
[Voice call invitation from Jason]

15:07.360 --> 15:07.960
Hello.

15:08.960 --> 15:09.790
Jason, where are you?

15:09.790 --> 15:11.120
I'll arrive at the club soon.

15:11.120 --> 15:12.720
Wait for me for a few minutes.

15:15.630 --> 15:16.320
Jason.

16:17.900 --> 16:18.900
Wang Fa.

16:21.600 --> 16:24.240
I entrusted my child to you.

16:29.030 --> 16:31.790
Did you really take good care of him?

16:58.080 --> 17:00.410
The last call he made
before he passed away

17:03.120 --> 17:04.440
was to me.

17:06.589 --> 17:07.920
But I couldn't save him.

17:12.250 --> 17:14.329
So I swore to find out

17:14.349 --> 17:16.550
who gave him the banned drugs.

17:22.359 --> 17:25.730
I put all the blame on others

17:27.920 --> 17:29.920
to ease my own guilt.

17:30.880 --> 17:32.110
Ridiculous, right?

17:32.580 --> 17:33.840
What about the police?

17:34.720 --> 17:36.450
Didn't they help investigate?

17:36.720 --> 17:39.580
His mother didn't want to
cause him secondary harm.

17:40.480 --> 17:41.720
No autopsy was done.

17:41.720 --> 17:43.200
It was ruled a suicide.

17:43.200 --> 17:44.240
Even so,

17:46.200 --> 17:47.590
it's not your fault.

17:49.570 --> 17:50.920
You can't give up on your life

17:50.920 --> 17:52.920
just because of him.

18:01.490 --> 18:03.600
This is his diary his mother gave me.

18:05.240 --> 18:07.170
After reading it, I don't think so.

18:13.050 --> 18:14.070
[During the training in the park today,
some high school students]

18:14.100 --> 18:15.290
[provoked me by saying I am bad at
playing soccer and asked me to get lost.]

18:17.400 --> 18:18.890
[One day, I'll prove myself
with my skills.]

18:18.240 --> 18:21.090
He was a very serious and ambitious boy.

18:18.910 --> 18:21.160
[Mr. Wang is great. I want to prove myself
with my skills like him.]

18:24.270 --> 18:25.260
[I haven't written my diary
for two months. I don't have enough time.]

18:25.280 --> 18:26.350
[I'm under a lot of pressure.
I got food poisoning last week.]

18:25.640 --> 18:28.440
He was very strict with himself.

18:26.380 --> 18:27.200
[I took two days off.
During this week's training,]

18:27.230 --> 18:28.230
[everyone seems to be better except me.
I can't fall behind.]

18:30.350 --> 18:31.350
So I took his behavior

18:30.670 --> 18:31.790
[Another teammate left today.
Coach didn't say much about it.]

18:31.350 --> 18:33.680
for granted.

18:31.820 --> 18:33.050
[I know he was eliminated by the club.]

18:33.070 --> 18:34.760
[The manager said that
competition is a purifier.]

18:37.650 --> 18:39.190
[But I felt tired when answering
Mom's video call.]

18:38.720 --> 18:41.070
He rarely confided his own things to me,

18:39.210 --> 18:41.310
[She mumbled a lot and just wanted
me to get a good result.]

18:41.340 --> 18:43.180
[I can't let my family look down on me.
I want to win, too.]

18:41.850 --> 18:45.080
and I never thought about
trying to understand him more.

18:45.110 --> 18:46.750
Coach said I was not
in good condition today.

18:46.750 --> 18:47.550
So I took

18:47.550 --> 18:49.400
-his silence as his prudence.
-He asked me if I had enough sleep

18:49.400 --> 18:51.030
and if I was uncomfortable.

18:51.030 --> 18:52.240
But that wasn't the case.

18:51.480 --> 18:52.530
[How could prohibited ingredients
be detected]

18:52.240 --> 18:53.440
I didn't dare to tell the truth.

18:52.550 --> 18:53.860
[from my blood? I've never used it.]

18:53.830 --> 18:55.690
He was just a child who needed

18:53.890 --> 18:54.870
[Did I eat anything wrong?]

18:55.720 --> 18:57.480
care, comfort, and attention.

18:57.480 --> 18:58.640
I was expelled.

18:58.640 --> 19:01.370
-I only put pressure on him
-Why didn't Mr. Wang trust me?

19:00.930 --> 19:03.200
[Why don't you trust me?]

19:01.400 --> 19:03.590
-brought him pain.
-Why don't you trust me?

19:03.590 --> 19:05.440
I know he trusted me

19:03.820 --> 19:04.890
[Why don't you trust me?
Why don't you trust me?]

19:05.440 --> 19:07.400
even more than he trusted himself.

19:10.720 --> 19:12.450
[Why don't you trust me?]

19:18.200 --> 19:20.120
Before he jumped off the roof,

19:21.750 --> 19:23.350
he must have struggled a lot.

19:25.880 --> 19:27.960
When everyone didn't trust him,

19:31.030 --> 19:33.310
I was the one who should
have trusted him the most,

19:33.310 --> 19:34.270
but I didn't.

19:38.240 --> 19:39.680
I actually doubted him.

19:43.400 --> 19:45.150
He saw me as a beacon,

19:45.920 --> 19:47.480
but I didn't light him up.

19:50.590 --> 19:51.790
His mother was right.

19:57.750 --> 19:59.750
I killed Jason.

20:34.240 --> 20:35.000
How did Jason

20:36.270 --> 20:38.310
become like this step by step?

20:40.000 --> 20:41.530
Shouldn't football itself

20:42.920 --> 20:45.270
bring joy and hope?

20:48.310 --> 20:50.110
I spent more than half of my life

20:51.830 --> 20:53.680
on football.

20:55.510 --> 20:57.270
But it wasn't until I was thirty

20:59.510 --> 21:02.100
that I realized in our industry,

21:02.310 --> 21:05.400
effort and time

21:06.400 --> 21:07.730
are the least valuable.

21:08.920 --> 21:11.250
Out of a hundred players who enter Nanton,

21:13.160 --> 21:15.550
maybe only one will remain at last.

21:16.680 --> 21:17.790
In this process,

21:19.030 --> 21:20.790
I have to constantly and very quickly

21:20.790 --> 21:22.880
abandon any player who can't keep up.

21:25.320 --> 21:27.320
Under this high-pressure system of

21:27.350 --> 21:29.550
eliminating the worthless,

21:30.590 --> 21:32.110
no one can bear it,

21:32.110 --> 21:34.130
Let alone a proud,

21:34.440 --> 21:35.880
and sensitive young man.

21:41.030 --> 21:42.160
I often feel that

21:43.350 --> 21:45.270
under the banner of the club,

21:47.640 --> 21:48.830
we are like warriors

21:48.830 --> 21:50.960
united under a primitive totem.

21:52.720 --> 21:54.310
It's just a different way.

21:55.000 --> 21:56.200
For money

21:56.920 --> 21:57.880
and victory,

21:59.830 --> 22:01.350
we fight the opponent.

22:05.060 --> 22:07.060
Are you questioning yourself?

22:09.960 --> 22:10.680
Yes.

22:11.680 --> 22:13.080
I am questioning myself.

22:15.960 --> 22:17.960
To be faster, higher, and stronger,

22:18.550 --> 22:19.920
for self-improvement,

22:20.510 --> 22:22.310
for transcending human limits,

22:22.640 --> 22:23.920
and for these interests,

22:23.920 --> 22:25.400
I ignored my players

22:26.640 --> 22:27.440
and made them victims

22:27.440 --> 22:28.880
in the Colosseum.

22:32.640 --> 22:34.790
I found myself repulsive.

22:41.640 --> 22:43.030
Can anyone tell me

22:47.350 --> 22:49.310
what on earth I am doing?

23:09.440 --> 23:10.400
I should go.

23:19.030 --> 23:20.030
I understand you.

23:25.180 --> 23:26.140
I know that

23:26.470 --> 23:27.600
before this,

23:28.830 --> 23:30.960
many people must have said this to you.

23:33.070 --> 23:34.800
But I still want to tell you that

23:35.510 --> 23:36.970
I understand how you feel.

23:45.350 --> 23:46.160
To be honest,

23:48.510 --> 23:50.110
on my way to find you,

23:52.000 --> 23:54.200
I thought of many conversation skills.

23:55.590 --> 23:56.920
But now I find that

23:59.810 --> 24:01.700
in the face of real problems,

24:02.750 --> 24:04.400
everything seems so barren.

24:10.310 --> 24:11.590
You can laugh at me.

24:13.750 --> 24:15.030
About a year ago,

24:16.510 --> 24:18.080
I was really in a bad state.

24:20.510 --> 24:22.440
I also reached a very high place.

24:32.150 --> 24:33.230
Heads,

24:34.160 --> 24:35.510
I go ahead.

24:36.110 --> 24:37.270
Tails,

24:37.790 --> 24:39.160
I stay.

24:48.240 --> 24:49.770
At that time, I thought that

24:50.350 --> 24:52.010
life was really meaningless.

24:54.810 --> 24:56.610
In the future, whether it's good

24:56.730 --> 24:57.840
or bad,

24:59.640 --> 25:01.770
I don't want to experience it anymore.

25:05.000 --> 25:06.370
You are the same, right?

25:07.580 --> 25:09.030
Do you also feel

25:10.720 --> 25:12.450
that football is meaningless?

25:20.930 --> 25:21.820
I don't know.

25:32.480 --> 25:33.330
Here you go.

25:36.240 --> 25:37.310
A coin toss.

25:39.350 --> 25:42.350
You use a coin
to choose sides in soccer.

25:43.370 --> 25:44.370
At that time,

25:44.810 --> 25:46.920
I happened to have a coin in my pocket.

25:47.960 --> 25:49.310
So I made a decision.

25:50.960 --> 25:51.960
Heads, I leave.

25:52.960 --> 25:53.830
Tails, I stay.

26:00.860 --> 26:03.120
I know I might not be
able to convince you.

26:04.370 --> 26:05.770
But I always feel

26:06.750 --> 26:08.200
that deep down,

26:12.430 --> 26:13.960
you are reluctant to let go.

26:16.700 --> 26:18.630
Don't ignore

26:18.680 --> 26:21.410
that little bit of reluctance
left in your heart.

26:21.440 --> 26:23.000
All your emotions

26:25.590 --> 26:27.030
are precious.

27:48.050 --> 27:49.120
Which side did you

27:49.960 --> 27:51.000
flip at that time?

28:06.000 --> 28:06.850
Heads.

28:10.830 --> 28:12.090
But you're still here.

28:13.940 --> 28:14.740
Because

28:16.080 --> 28:17.120
I cheated.

28:20.260 --> 28:26.330
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

28:27.010 --> 28:31.680
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

28:33.380 --> 28:38.730
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

28:39.490 --> 28:45.270
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

28:41.310 --> 28:42.450
Ms. Lin.

28:42.470 --> 28:44.320
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

28:44.350 --> 28:46.140
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

28:46.160 --> 28:47.790
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

28:46.520 --> 28:52.330
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

28:47.790 --> 28:49.640
-Get up, Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

28:49.640 --> 28:51.000
Are you still sleeping?

28:51.000 --> 28:52.210
Ms. Lin.

28:52.230 --> 28:53.960
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

28:53.120 --> 28:57.940
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

28:53.960 --> 28:54.480
Ms. Lin!

28:54.480 --> 28:55.510
Let's go.

28:59.550 --> 29:04.990
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

29:01.400 --> 29:02.030
It's so hot.

29:02.030 --> 29:02.830
Take it easy.

29:04.110 --> 29:06.500
I only brought a scallion pancake.

29:05.850 --> 29:10.560
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

29:06.680 --> 29:09.830
I also brought some fruits as
I'm afraid other foods are hard to digest.

29:09.830 --> 29:10.590
It's early in the morning.

29:10.590 --> 29:12.070
Are you preparing a state banquet?

29:11.870 --> 29:14.980
♪ The love I gave ♪

29:13.680 --> 29:15.240
Don't you know what day it is today?

29:15.240 --> 29:18.350
Today is the third round
of Group A in the Champions League.

29:18.350 --> 29:20.050
Watch to learn something.

29:20.080 --> 29:20.880
Come on, Ms. Lin.

29:20.880 --> 29:21.590
Open it.

29:21.590 --> 29:22.830
Come on.

29:24.030 --> 29:25.790
-Let's enable screen mirroring.
-Come on. Let me enable screen mirroring.

29:25.790 --> 29:27.400
Come on, open it.

29:27.400 --> 29:28.240
Okay.

29:30.240 --> 29:34.110
-Okay. Here we go. Begin.
-Come on.

29:34.390 --> 29:35.550
-Here we go.
-Nice shot!

29:35.550 --> 29:37.030
-Nice shot!
-I can do this kick too.

29:37.030 --> 29:39.360
Boss, you are overestimating yourself.

29:40.030 --> 29:41.270
If you practiced from birth,

29:41.270 --> 29:42.110
maybe you could.

29:42.110 --> 29:43.510
Let me ask you a question.

29:45.510 --> 29:48.240
Why do you insist on watching
the game at my place?

29:49.640 --> 29:50.680
Since Coach left,

29:50.680 --> 29:52.110
Qin Ao was afraid you'd be lonely.

29:52.110 --> 29:54.750
Then, he called all of us here
to keep you company.

29:54.750 --> 29:56.680
It wasn't me.

29:56.680 --> 29:57.480
It was Fu.

29:58.400 --> 29:59.960
-No.
-No.

30:01.070 --> 30:03.200
We were just afraid you'd be sad alone.

30:06.030 --> 30:07.750
Thank you for your concern.

30:07.750 --> 30:10.080
But don't you guys read the forum?

30:10.100 --> 30:10.770
-Forum.
-Forum. Forum.

30:10.770 --> 30:12.230
-What forum?
-What forum?

30:12.680 --> 30:14.640
-Have a look.
-Enable screen mirroring.

30:14.640 --> 30:15.640
-Coming.
-Here.

30:16.400 --> 30:18.070
Insider news.

30:18.070 --> 30:22.640
The head coach of Yongchuan Hengjiu Club
is settled,

30:27.440 --> 30:28.280
[Breaking news! According to
the member of Yongchuan Hengjiu,]

30:28.300 --> 30:29.240
[they want the former vice-director of
the training camp of Nanton,]

30:28.680 --> 30:30.240
Winfred.

30:29.260 --> 30:30.140
[a young coach named Winfred.]

30:32.270 --> 30:34.530
Yongchuan Hengjiu Club poached our guy.

30:34.540 --> 30:36.150
If I get rich one day,

30:36.340 --> 30:37.600
I'll poach Coach back.

30:40.000 --> 30:41.120
Scroll down more.

30:43.020 --> 30:43.550
[Internal information! The head coach
of Yongchuan Hengjiu has been selected.]

30:43.640 --> 30:44.670
[Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club]

30:44.690 --> 30:46.120
[appoint Liu Chuanguang
as the head coach of Team 1]

30:45.370 --> 30:47.850
Yongchuan Hengjiu Football Club

30:47.880 --> 30:51.240
appoints Liu Chuanguang
as the head coach of the first team.

30:51.240 --> 30:53.400
Yongchuan Hengjiu Club finally
chose Coach Liu.

30:53.400 --> 30:54.680
What about our coach?

30:54.680 --> 30:56.510
He couldn't have gone
back to Nanton, right?

30:56.510 --> 30:57.310
Where did our coach go?

30:57.310 --> 30:58.430
Where is our coach?

30:59.200 --> 31:00.590
-Who? Who?
-Someone is knocking.

31:00.590 --> 31:02.240
-Someone is knocking.
-Who?

31:02.640 --> 31:04.070
I also ordered takeout.

31:05.190 --> 31:06.800
Slide down.

31:07.060 --> 31:08.060
Don't worry.

31:08.400 --> 31:09.680
Why?

31:10.300 --> 31:13.070
-Is it true?
-It should be true.

31:14.000 --> 31:14.640
It's official.

31:14.640 --> 31:15.790
Take a look at where the coach went.

31:15.790 --> 31:16.830
-Official.
-Yes.

31:17.640 --> 31:19.030
It's really Liu Chuanguang.

31:19.030 --> 31:19.750
What does it mean?

31:19.750 --> 31:22.480
-It's Liu Chuanguang.
-Why is it Liu Chuanguang?

31:23.830 --> 31:25.070
So many food.

31:25.070 --> 31:27.000
I wouldn't have bought it if I knew.

31:31.440 --> 31:34.680
Coach!

31:37.350 --> 31:38.750
You haven't left?

31:38.750 --> 31:40.590
No.
Coach.

31:41.030 --> 31:42.000
You are...

31:41.740 --> 31:43.360
♪ Your voice is like the wind ♪

31:43.920 --> 31:44.790
Coach.

31:44.240 --> 31:45.970
♪ Things will eventually change ♪

31:45.790 --> 31:47.200
You're still here

31:47.200 --> 31:50.230
♪ You're still obsessed with me♪

31:48.550 --> 31:50.610
Since you don't want me here, I'll go.

31:50.890 --> 31:52.040
♪ Those surging secrets ♪

31:50.970 --> 31:52.630
No, Coach. Sit.

31:52.630 --> 31:54.620
♪ You hid in my eyes ♪

31:52.660 --> 31:53.590
Wait, Coach.

31:53.590 --> 31:55.510
Did Yongchuan Hengjiu reject you?

31:55.450 --> 31:58.300
♪ I witnessed your persistence ♪

31:56.390 --> 31:58.680
Weren't you poached?

31:58.990 --> 32:00.430
♪ The change will come true ♪

32:00.070 --> 32:01.830
After careful consideration,

32:01.040 --> 32:02.920
♪ I've seen it clearly ♪

32:01.830 --> 32:03.440
I think you brats

32:03.440 --> 32:04.270
are much more interesting.

32:04.080 --> 32:06.650
♪ The situation by your side ♪

32:04.270 --> 32:05.880
Who are you calling brats?

32:06.230 --> 32:08.270
Coach, let me ask you.

32:07.450 --> 32:08.960
♪ I give up the past ♪

32:08.270 --> 32:10.590
Why did you suddenly change your mind?

32:09.490 --> 32:12.180
♪ Our true selves ♪

32:10.590 --> 32:11.360
Yeah.

32:11.880 --> 32:13.920
I told you I couldn't
bear to leave you guys.

32:13.210 --> 32:15.330
♪ I can't persistent any longer ♪

32:16.270 --> 32:17.520
♪ High in the sky ♪

32:17.110 --> 32:18.720
Coach, could you not bear to leave us

32:18.420 --> 32:19.800
♪ You know how I feel ♪

32:18.720 --> 32:19.590
or…

32:19.590 --> 32:21.110
Could you really not bear to leave us...

32:20.670 --> 32:21.600
♪ Will I become you ♪

32:21.110 --> 32:23.160
Or Ms. Lin?

32:22.650 --> 32:24.200
♪ I want to be myself ♪

32:24.960 --> 32:26.180
♪ If time can reach ♪

32:25.030 --> 32:26.960
I really couldn't bear
to leave her either.

32:26.960 --> 32:28.270
♪ I will remove all the deception ♪

32:29.090 --> 32:30.710
♪ If you follow your heart ♪

32:29.640 --> 32:31.830
What, do I not deserve it?

32:31.740 --> 32:33.240
♪ The ending is predestined ♪

32:31.850 --> 32:33.030
Of course you do.

32:33.060 --> 32:34.560
-Of course.
-You are the best in the world.

32:33.990 --> 32:35.540
♪ The change will come true ♪

32:34.590 --> 32:36.590
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

32:36.490 --> 32:38.180
♪ I've seen it clearly ♪

32:36.590 --> 32:37.830
Since Coach isn't leaving,

32:37.830 --> 32:39.750
let's have hot pot for lunch to celebrate.

32:38.670 --> 32:41.610
♪ The situation by your side ♪

32:39.750 --> 32:42.590
Sure.
I haven't had hotpot for a long time.

32:42.530 --> 32:43.830
♪ I give up the past ♪

32:42.590 --> 32:44.510
Since you suggested it, it's your treat.

32:44.510 --> 32:45.640
Right, your treat.

32:44.560 --> 32:47.110
♪ Our true selves ♪

32:45.640 --> 32:47.400
The place we saved last time.
Let's go there.

32:47.400 --> 32:48.350
At the school gate.

32:47.870 --> 32:50.070
♪ I can't persistent any longer ♪

32:48.350 --> 32:49.400
How much is it?

32:49.400 --> 32:51.310
-No.
-Can you afford it, Qin Ao?

32:51.150 --> 32:52.400
♪ High in the sky ♪

32:52.750 --> 32:53.960
Coach won't leave, so he should treat.

32:53.040 --> 32:54.540
♪ You know how I feel ♪

32:53.960 --> 32:55.310
I'll return it to you

32:55.670 --> 32:56.620
♪ Will I become you ♪

32:56.160 --> 32:57.750
Please, Coach.
Right?

32:57.420 --> 32:58.860
♪ I want to be myself ♪

32:59.660 --> 33:01.040
♪ If time can reach ♪

33:02.000 --> 33:03.080
♪ I will remove all the deception ♪

33:04.150 --> 33:05.410
♪ If you follow your heart ♪

33:04.640 --> 33:05.680
It's my treat.

33:05.680 --> 33:06.920
I'll treat.

33:06.910 --> 33:10.380
♪ The ending is predestined ♪

33:07.590 --> 33:08.990
Who exactly is treating?

33:12.030 --> 33:13.070
To be honest,

33:13.400 --> 33:14.570
I think the decision you made

33:14.570 --> 33:15.900
is absolutely correct.

33:16.640 --> 33:17.790
Don't worry about anything else.

33:17.790 --> 33:18.590
The most important thing

33:18.590 --> 33:20.400
is to get your life back on track.

33:21.480 --> 33:23.010
I must have told you before.

33:23.480 --> 33:25.310
When you speak to me like an elder,

33:25.310 --> 33:26.910
you're asking for a beating.

33:26.920 --> 33:28.780
Is that how you talk to your elder?

33:29.030 --> 33:30.240
I am your brother-in-law.

33:30.240 --> 33:32.100
That makes me half an elder to you.

33:37.830 --> 33:38.590
So...

33:40.020 --> 33:40.870
So...

33:42.780 --> 33:44.450
Did you tell Lin Wanxing

33:44.480 --> 33:46.340
everything about the situation?

33:48.910 --> 33:50.580
I'm curious, wasn't she angry?

33:50.580 --> 33:53.390
Didn't she push you off the roof?

33:55.350 --> 33:56.730
Not exactly everything.

33:56.730 --> 33:59.210
Okay, don't say anything. Let me guess.

34:00.030 --> 34:01.030
You told her everything

34:01.030 --> 34:02.270
about Jason.

34:03.240 --> 34:04.400
But you didn't tell her

34:04.400 --> 34:06.550
that you came to Hongjing

34:06.940 --> 34:08.469
to investigate her, right?

34:17.110 --> 34:18.800
Bro, listen to me.

34:20.030 --> 34:21.830
If you keep hiding this from her,

34:22.030 --> 34:23.360
it will end badly.

34:23.360 --> 34:24.360
Don't I know that?

34:24.880 --> 34:26.150
Then what will you do?

34:26.150 --> 34:27.610
You can't hide it forever.

34:32.630 --> 34:34.090
Even if she knew the truth,

34:35.070 --> 34:36.929
she wouldn't push me off the roof.

34:37.190 --> 34:38.719
She would just push me away.

34:39.110 --> 34:40.310
I want that even less.

34:47.000 --> 34:48.110
So I can only wait.

34:49.280 --> 34:51.030
I can only explain it to her

34:51.760 --> 34:54.090
after I investigate everything clearly.

34:57.680 --> 34:59.410
Is there any progress in the UK?

35:01.000 --> 35:02.000
Yes.

35:03.280 --> 35:05.030
Every time his team pulls off

35:05.030 --> 35:06.570
such an abnormal upset,

35:06.620 --> 35:09.280
Kevin makes a huge expenditure.

35:09.280 --> 35:13.700
The luxury cars, yachts, and real estate
under his name

35:13.720 --> 35:16.040
all exceed his financial capacity.

35:18.480 --> 35:21.000
Why didn't you mention
such important progress earlier?

35:21.000 --> 35:22.000
Are you kidding me?

35:22.000 --> 35:23.480
I was caring for my junior,

35:23.480 --> 35:25.340
and doing what an elder should do.

35:27.440 --> 35:28.440
So, he...

35:29.110 --> 35:30.400
He has the profit

35:30.710 --> 35:31.730
and the motive.

35:32.360 --> 35:33.400
Now we only lack

35:33.400 --> 35:34.860
his connection to Spade Q.

35:36.990 --> 35:38.430
As for the rest,

35:39.480 --> 35:41.080
we are still investigating.

36:03.270 --> 36:04.830
[A gift for Wang Fa's returning]

36:55.450 --> 36:58.780
[Superstar Slacker]

36:58.970 --> 37:03.130
Thanks, this one looks...

37:05.840 --> 37:09.370
It looks a lot like you. Welcome back
to the Little Savage Tribe.

37:45.430 --> 37:46.960
[Zhou Hui]

38:04.670 --> 38:05.470
Wait a minute.

38:07.030 --> 38:07.880
Go easy on me,

38:07.880 --> 38:09.150
Wen Chengye.

38:10.170 --> 38:11.320
You're on duty today.

38:11.320 --> 38:12.640
Be a good boy.

38:13.030 --> 38:13.960
Likewise,

38:14.230 --> 38:15.560
the Queen of Being Late.

38:16.080 --> 38:17.410
It's not time yet, is it?

38:21.720 --> 38:22.530
Now it is.

38:23.440 --> 38:24.150
Congratulations,

38:24.150 --> 38:24.970
you're late again.

38:24.970 --> 38:27.970
Your morality points
should be fully deducted by now.

38:28.440 --> 38:29.690
Likewise.

38:42.670 --> 38:43.440
Thanks.

39:12.660 --> 39:13.620
Thank you.

39:13.670 --> 39:15.130
You really helped me a lot.

39:16.050 --> 39:17.890
Are you a teacher here too?

39:24.190 --> 39:26.480
Li, are you Ju Li?

39:28.100 --> 39:30.300
Good thing you still remember the code.

39:34.100 --> 39:35.560
Long time no see, Wanxing.

39:36.670 --> 39:38.150
It really is you.

39:40.920 --> 39:43.110
Li, why are you at
Hongjing No. 8 High School?

39:43.110 --> 39:44.800
Today is my first day of work.

39:45.080 --> 39:46.220
Work?

39:46.460 --> 39:48.260
We'll be colleagues from now on.

39:48.480 --> 39:49.480
Deskmates in middle school,

39:49.480 --> 39:50.440
now colleagues.

39:50.440 --> 39:52.150
You can't get rid of me in the future.

39:52.150 --> 39:53.550
That's great.

39:53.820 --> 39:55.550
I'm going to a meeting. And you?

39:55.670 --> 39:56.920
I'll report to the grade group first,

39:56.920 --> 39:57.880
then go to class.

39:58.840 --> 39:59.840
I'll come find you later.

39:59.840 --> 40:00.320
I'm running out of time.

40:00.320 --> 40:01.030
I'll go first.

40:01.030 --> 40:01.480
Okay.

40:06.760 --> 40:07.800
Did you guys hear?

40:07.800 --> 40:09.800
A new teacher seems to have
come to our grade group,

40:09.800 --> 40:11.710
said to be a physics genius

40:11.960 --> 40:13.960
who made the national
Physics Olympiad Team.

40:13.960 --> 40:15.670
She seems to have graduated from
an Ivy League university.

40:15.670 --> 40:16.710
Come on.

40:17.320 --> 40:19.850
What kind of big genius
would come to our dump?

40:20.280 --> 40:21.480
Even so, bro,

40:21.480 --> 40:22.590
we will have the best coach

40:22.590 --> 40:23.550
and the best teacher.

40:23.550 --> 40:24.400
-Yeah.
-That's an amazing and cool place.

40:24.400 --> 40:26.800
The amazing Hongjing No. 8 High School
emerged from nowhere.

40:26.800 --> 40:28.360
I hope so.

40:28.360 --> 40:29.110
Zhi Hui is telling the fortune again.

40:29.110 --> 40:31.910
Why don't you calculate
how the Feng Shui is today?

40:32.280 --> 40:33.810
We'll get scolded by Coach.

40:34.840 --> 40:35.280
Stop.

40:38.030 --> 40:39.110
What's going on?

40:39.630 --> 40:41.960
I've been too gentle with you lately, huh?

40:41.980 --> 40:43.440
How is that possible, Coach?

40:43.440 --> 40:44.760
A misunderstanding of 'gentle'.

40:44.760 --> 40:46.000
After finishing this,

40:46.000 --> 40:47.440
do two more sets of endurance training.

40:47.440 --> 40:49.190
Coach, our legs are almost dead.

40:49.190 --> 40:49.960
Three sets.

40:52.280 --> 40:53.510
Three sets.

40:53.510 --> 40:53.800
Okay.

40:53.800 --> 40:54.590
Three sets.

40:54.590 --> 40:56.030
What a coincidence.

40:56.030 --> 40:57.150
-Go on.
-I didn't expect

40:57.150 --> 40:58.680
you to come teach here, too.

40:58.710 --> 41:00.320
See those little blue elves?

41:00.320 --> 41:01.360
Come on, next set, get ready.

41:01.360 --> 41:03.000
Let me officially introduce them to you.

41:03.000 --> 41:04.920
They are members of
the football team I lead.

41:04.920 --> 41:06.280
And the guy in the knit sweateris

41:06.280 --> 41:07.150
their coach,

41:07.150 --> 41:08.230
Wang Fa. Let's go.

41:08.230 --> 41:09.230
Let me introduce.

41:10.590 --> 41:12.000
This is my good friend Ju Li.

41:12.000 --> 41:13.280
She also came to our school to teach.

41:13.280 --> 41:14.480
She teaches physics.

41:14.710 --> 41:15.920
Hello, Coach Wang.

41:15.920 --> 41:16.670
I am Ju Li,

41:17.070 --> 41:18.630
Wanxing's childhood friend.

41:18.630 --> 41:19.400
Wang Fa.

41:20.920 --> 41:21.670
By the way, Wanxing,

41:21.670 --> 41:22.840
I need to head back to the team first.

41:22.840 --> 41:24.710
They want me to give a report.

41:24.710 --> 41:27.000
Anyway, just don't forget about Saturday.

41:27.000 --> 41:28.510
Got it. Go ahead.

41:28.510 --> 41:30.110
You have plans for Saturday?

41:30.280 --> 41:32.630
Yeah, Li planned to take me camping

41:32.630 --> 41:33.920
to get close to nature.

41:35.030 --> 41:37.630
Didn't we agree to have
roast duck on Saturday?

41:37.800 --> 41:38.760
Yes.

41:38.760 --> 41:40.320
How about Sunday?

41:40.710 --> 41:41.500
But

41:42.230 --> 41:44.710
didn't you promise to take me
shopping on Sunday?

41:44.710 --> 41:45.630
I just got here.

41:47.880 --> 41:49.350
Look at my bad memory.

41:49.590 --> 41:51.780
How about we go next week?

41:51.960 --> 41:53.920
A restaurant can be booked anytime, right?

41:53.920 --> 41:55.840
When are you going to have roast duck?

41:55.840 --> 41:57.320
I like it, too. Let's go together.

41:57.320 --> 41:59.190
Sure. Let's go together.

41:59.190 --> 42:00.590
My treat as an apology.

42:01.070 --> 42:03.030
Great. Then I'll go camping too.

42:05.280 --> 42:06.410
I like camping, too.

42:15.710 --> 42:18.840
I think camping is more
fun with more people.

42:19.230 --> 42:21.830
Then let's go together with Li.

42:24.920 --> 42:26.320
Sure. If you're okay,

42:26.320 --> 42:27.320
I'm fine with it.

42:31.840 --> 42:33.040
I'll get back to work.

42:38.630 --> 42:40.230
Three more sets of training.

42:40.400 --> 42:41.460
Don't be like this.

42:49.840 --> 42:50.630
Wanxing.

42:50.650 --> 42:52.780
-Is that heavy? Let me help you.
-Here.

42:53.110 --> 42:54.030
Thank you.

42:57.280 --> 42:58.880
You guys are so nice.

42:59.840 --> 43:01.570
Felix Yu said he's almost here.

43:06.450 --> 43:07.250
They're here.

43:13.590 --> 43:14.630
Why are you here?

43:17.480 --> 43:18.880
Miss Celeste?

43:18.880 --> 43:20.030
My name is Wang Tian.

43:20.150 --> 43:20.800
Ms. Lin.

43:20.800 --> 43:21.630
We meet again.

43:35.820 --> 43:37.100
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

43:38.290 --> 43:39.620
♪ Because you're with me ♪

43:42.770 --> 43:44.020
♪ The light shimmers ♪
